    "body": "I understand why it's happening, but feel it shouldn't. I feel `#[should_fail]` should change the test runner's behavior to \"I expect that this test will panic for each `assert!`\"\n\nConsider it carefully. Is there any circumstance where you would want the current behavior rather than the proposed? I've shown how it can silently cause a problem.\n",
